\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/svitlana288/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee278aaedb0b81f188310ef0fbcc908c0edd72ce55e69200250b5712bd6b2aee?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee278aaedb0b81f188310ef0fbcc908c0edd72ce55e69200250b5712bd6b2aee?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/svitlana288/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">svitlana288</a> <span class=\"review-date\">16 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Great support!<br />They were patient, professional, and helped me identify the issue with my checkout page.<br />Thank you for your clear and kind assistance! 🙏<br />— Svitlana</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support for issue with Action Scheduler</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hjorth007/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c2d3c1ea60be7aaed9c350798777bea2eda8e5c213f8e7a1f7811f5d1970f461?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c2d3c1ea60be7aaed9c350798777bea2eda8e5c213f8e7a1f7811f5d1970f461?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hjorth007/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Hjorth007</a> <span class=\"review-date\">16 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I presented my problems and got a quick answer back, with back and forth questions and answers. Very serious and competent support. Woocommerce shop-system and support is second to none. :)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to Customise - Good to start with</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rajanrawal/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d3738b1507cfe07fd0223d35593256c28362850323033061a985d6f4c0664f7c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d3738b1507cfe07fd0223d35593256c28362850323033061a985d6f4c0664f7c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rajanrawal/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rajanrawal</a> <span class=\"review-date\">16 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is a great plugin for anyone starting out with WooCommerce. The customization options are straightforward and easy to understand, making it simple to get a professional-looking store up and running quickly. It’s perfect for a new user who wants to build a product page without getting bogged down in complex settings. Highly recommend for its user-friendly interface.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Relativamente fácil de usar, incluso para principiantes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/novoidoso/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d43137338816787442f1fd5e897938944071c5079556a032d68d4ec8b92e60dc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d43137338816787442f1fd5e897938944071c5079556a032d68d4ec8b92e60dc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/novoidoso/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">novoidoso</a> <span class=\"review-date\">15 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Soy nuevo en WordPress y WooCommerce fue mi primera experiencia creando una tienda online.<br />Me sorprendió lo intuitivo que es y cómo se puede configurar todo sin tener experiencia previa.<br />Excelente herramienta para empezar en el e-commerce.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Violates the GDPR and installs extra plugins without consent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/josklever/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c1f959fb0ddff6b3612c1ac23f3b8cd738ab5095b69bab5bc7f8627cbcbe8c6f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c1f959fb0ddff6b3612c1ac23f3b8cd738ab5095b69bab5bc7f8627cbcbe8c6f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/josklever/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jos Klever <small>(josklever)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">14 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During the onboarding wizard people often keep the default/recommended settings, but then they automatically \"agree\" to tracking and sharing data with third parties. That\'s a violation of the GDPR. People should actively and willingly agree to things like that.<br /><br />Users also get multiple plugins installed without much information and why they would need them (they don\'t, because there are alternatives). These plugins can be recommended, but users would need to choose to install them (opt-in) and not having to remove them.<br /><br />More than a year ago I contacted support because of other violations and 2 of the 4 were handled after multiple emails. The rest was ignored. After that no response...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">better than Amazons customer service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/beautysuppliesbylia/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4954b7189da64da0b1aa878ff78eacfd9cda4c79b38f0e94dd79db3ea872562?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4954b7189da64da0b1aa878ff78eacfd9cda4c79b38f0e94dd79db3ea872562?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/beautysuppliesbylia/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">beautysuppliesbylia</a> <span class=\"review-date\">14 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>unbelievable knowledge from both agents</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>fast response with 5 star instructions</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>no complaints at all</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Decent Plugin but Needs Some Improvements</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ericpearson148/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea811f2932d5a0b0144e73bc187d8476982aa7537720e90f7f21f94cdc693bd7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea811f2932d5a0b0144e73bc187d8476982aa7537720e90f7f21f94cdc693bd7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ericpearson148/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ericpearson148</a> <span class=\"review-date\">13 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I’ve been using <strong>[WooCommerce]</strong> for a few weeks now. The plugin does what it promises — it’s easy to set up and integrates nicely with my store. However, I did face a few minor issues with loading speed and customization options.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The basic features work fine, but I think it could be more polished, especially in terms of user experience and flexibility. Overall, it’s a decent plugin for beginners, but it still has room to grow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">ótimo pra loja mas tem uns bugs</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aldairalves/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/603b30b14d4bbaea97bcfcb551e17e885e3f8cbb522c04b64208d827a3fd8afe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/603b30b14d4bbaea97bcfcb551e17e885e3f8cbb522c04b64208d827a3fd8afe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aldairalves/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aldairalves</a> <span class=\"review-date\">8 октября, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>to usando o WooCommerce faz um tempo e gostei, ele ajuda mto a montar a loja e gerenciar os produtos. tem umas coisa q bugam as vezes e da trabalho, mas no geral funciona bem. se souber mexer da pra fazer coisa muito boa. recomendo pra quem ta começando 👍</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">An incredibly flexible and extensible platform!</h4>